Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:49.66,Karaoke2,,0000,0000,0000,,時には、本気で忘れられます　存在\Ntoki ni wa honki de wasureraremasu sonzai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I feel like people have totally forgotten about my existence
